<br>
Personally I believe Religion is a man made attempt to consume the ideal of what God is.  The Holy Roman Church did it with the europeans in the early days, converting thier pegan holy days into Christian semblances in order for them to accept the new God in place of thier own.  I think the error is when people associate God with the practices of manmade religion which are simpy an attempt to rationalize God in a consumable manner for the masses.  God is a personal thing.... religion is not.<br>
<br>
